<div class="container">
  <br>

  <div id="how-to">
    <div class="homepage">
      <span><%= image_tag("echtsquarelogo.png", alt: "Echtchange", style: "display: block; width: 115px; margin: 0 auto;") %></span>
      <h2>How Do I Get Started?</h2>
      <hr>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <p>You're signed in! Check out the info below on how Echtchange works!</p>
      <% else %>
        <p>Check out the info below on how Echtchange works! If you'd like to begin buying and/or selling books, click the link below to sign up with your Princeton email!</p>
        <br>
        <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg", style: "display: block; width: 130px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Avenir Next;" %>
      <% end %>
      <br>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br>

  <div id="why-us">
    <h2>Our Simple Process</h2>
    <hr>
    <div class="center">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
            <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-pencil fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
          </span>
          <h3>Browse</h3>
          <p>Quickly search for your book by Course Subject from the navbar and find the best deals on your books. All without having to make an account!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
            <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-users fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
          </span>
          <h3>Buy</h3>
          <p>Buy your book on our site, recieve an email when it has arrived and pick it up from an Echtchange representative in Frist. It's that easy!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
            <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-money fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
          </span>
          <h3>Sell</h3>
          <p>Post your book listing on our site, receive an email when it is sold, drop it off with an Echtchange representative in Frist, and immediately receive a Venmo for cash for your sold book.</p>
        </div>
      </div>   
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
</div>